@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((0.07 - 0.97) + (wp.sin(v2 + 0.75) - (tmp + 0.37 - v2 + 0.13)))
    v2 = 0.76
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v2 + 0.90 / v2 + 0.59)))
    tmp = v1
    v1 = (wp.abs(0.98) * ((v1 + 0.35 - v2 + 0.33) / (v1 + 0.35 + tmp + 0.47)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.56)))
    data[tid] = v0
